        <h3 class="section-heading">Description</h3>
        <div class="container printshow">
           
            <p>Three of the world's leading technology companies collaborated to build the world's leading tablet experience. Featuring the best that Lenovo, Microsoft and Intel have to offer, the ThinkPad Tablet 2 redefines business, appeasing IT manager and end user alike in one productive, mobile, reliable device.</p>                        
            
            

