                <h3>Summary</h3>
                <div class="container printshow">
                    <dl>
<dt>Product Description</dt>
<dd>Lenovo ThinkPad Tablet 2 3679 - 10.1&quot; - Atom Z2760 - Windows 8 32-bit - 32 GB Flash - 2 GB RAM</dd>
</dl>
